      <div class="modal-body">
        <img src="/images/bafaVision.jpg" alt="Success Story Image" style="width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
        <p><strong>Published:</strong> July 21, 2023</p>

        <p>As Melba continues to grow, it’s clear: our next chapter is bold, intentional, and community-first. With renewed momentum and visionary leadership, we're moving into an exciting new era of impact.</p>

        <p>Rather than focusing on numbers or headlines, we're focusing on the <em>why</em>—the people behind the programs and the purpose that drives them. This isn't just about expanding services. It's about reimagining what's possible for youth and young adults across Seattle.</p>

        <h6 class="mt-3">🌟 Our Vision: Empowerment at Every Stage</h6>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Melba Tech Labs:</strong> A new generation of coding workshops and AI literacy bootcamps—led by tech mentors from Amazon, Microsoft, and Google.</li>
          <li><strong>Urban Wellness Circle:</strong> Mental health and mindfulness for youth of color, run by certified BIPOC therapists.</li>
          <li><strong>Melba+ Career Pathways:</strong> Apprenticeships and shadowing opportunities with Seattle's top industries—from maritime to green energy.</li>
        </ul>

        <img src="/images/bafaLeadership.jpg" alt="Success Story Image" style="width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 10px;">

        <h6 class="mt-3">🌱 Our Core Leadership Values</h6>
        <img src="/images/community.jpg" alt="Core Leadership" style="float: right; max-width: 40%; margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Community-first:</strong> We listen before we lead. Youth voices guide our direction.</li>
          <li><strong>Cultural relevance:</strong> Our curriculum reflects who we serve—not just what we teach.</li>
          <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Programs are multilingual, hybrid, and free for all.</li>
          <li><strong>Leadership from within:</strong> Over 60% of Melba program leads are alumni, like Korme Kedir, who’ve walked the path themselves.</li>
        </ul>

        <h6 class="mt-3">🤝 Why Join Us?</h6>
